GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_ProductOverview> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_ProductOverview> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#ProductOverview> ;
    narr:childCount "17"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "d1b09a828565de86" ;
    narr:narration """The ProductOverview hub gathers the shape of the aswritten product across UX, architecture, packaging, pricing, and tooling. The architectural mainline argues a [single adaptive /mcp endpoint](narr:Narrative_AdaptiveToolsUX) beats per-repo server configs, with the [superiority claim](narr:Claim_AdaptiveToolsOverMultiServer) stated flatly. The internal tool stack — [worldview](narr:Observation_WorldviewTool) (identity/routing), [context](narr:Observation_ContextTool) (cheap structural index), [introspect-as-orchestrator](narr:Observation_IntrospectTool) — supports it. On packaging, the through-line moved from [starter perspectives as on-ramps not core](narr:Narrative_StarterPerspectivesAnalysis) (Mar) toward [prepackaged expertise modules](narr:Narrative_PrepackagedModuleConcept) (Mar), then to the [scarce-expert filter with goal-gated escalation](narr:Narrative_ScarceExpertFilterGoalGated) (Apr) that explicitly dissolves the 60-day ICP drift. Later threads layer on [per-project prompt extension](narr:Narrative_PerProjectPromptExtension) (May), [agent-as-analytics-interface](narr:Narrative_AgentAsAnalyticsInterface) (May), and a [personal worldview graph layer](narr:Narrative_PersonalGraphLayer). Pricing lands on [per-group subscription](narr:Pricing_PerGroupSubscription); [conviction levels](narr:Obs_ConvictionLevels) ship as a feature; the [YC app generated by AI](narr:Narrative_ProductAsProof) serves as product-as-proof.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_AdaptiveToolsOverMultiServer> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AdaptiveToolsUX> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AgentAsAnalyticsInterface> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_MultiRepoVision> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_PerProjectPromptExtension> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_PersonalGraphLayer> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_PrepackagedModuleConcept> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ProductAsProof> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ScarceExpertFilterGoalGated> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_StarterPerspectivesAnalysis> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ConvictionLevels> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_MultiRepoPlanted> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_ContextTool> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_IntrospectTool> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_WorldviewTool> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Pricing_PerGroupSubscription> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Product_SMSCollectiveMemory> ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "A single /mcp endpoint with adaptive tools is superior UX to separate MCP server configs per repo." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_AdaptiveToolsOverMultiServer> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "Starter perspectives are demos and on-ramps, not the core product." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_StarterPerspectivesAnalysis> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "This dissolves the earlier 60-day ICP drift (enterprise → SMB → B2C → transcripts)" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ScarceExpertFilterGoalGated> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "We want expertise in a worldview." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_PrepackagedModuleConcept> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "No app. No install. No login. No git. The product is a phone number." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Product_SMSCollectiveMemory> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "one shot and usable" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ProductAsProof> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Architectural fork: single adaptive /mcp endpoint that eliminates per-repo config friction vs. the multi-repo vision of separate scoped repos (strategy / QA / client-facing) — these pull in opposite directions on repo granularity." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AdaptiveToolsUX> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_AdaptiveToolsOverMultiServer> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_MultiRepoVision> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_MultiRepoPlanted> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Structurally distinct product shape: SMS-first collective memory — 'the product is a phone number,' no app/git/MCP — sits entirely outside the git/MCP/repo framing the rest of the hub assumes." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Product_SMSCollectiveMemory> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Road not taken, made explicit: usage visibility delivered through the agent interface rather than the 'traditional product' dashboard a request like the customer's CTO's would normally trigger." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AgentAsAnalyticsInterface> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Packaging tension: starter/generic perspectives have a weak purchase trigger and are framed as demos/on-ramps, while the core product is YOUR expertise — yet prepackaged modules pitch 'browse, install, verify' immediate value with no upfront building." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_StarterPerspectivesAnalysis> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_PrepackagedModuleConcept> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Pricing reversal flagged in-line: per-group subscription is 'back to pay-per-repo,' signaling an earlier pricing model was tried and abandoned." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Pricing_PerGroupSubscription> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Claimed-missing layer: the Solo/Parallel/Hub/Salon/Teams taxonomy is asserted to lack a personal-graph dimension, an outlier pushing beneath organizational memory." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_PersonalGraphLayer> ] ;
    narr:writer "claude (subscription)" .
}